########################             Description             ########################
#####################################################################################
         Edithosts is designed to strengthen the security and privacy of users.
    Edithosts increases the speed of surfing the Internet, blocks ads, tracking
                                and malware domains.


                       Edithosts works with /etc/hosts file.
